    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80ae-80a5-e4251f9137fd",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "TBL is commonly used to help individuals develop collaborative learning activities, but iterative TBL has been somewhat neglected in the literature. The authors introduce a framework for iterative TBL that sub-divides iterative TBL into 4 stages of group activity workflows and 3 data flows.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80ae-80a5-e4251f9137fd",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
