              "text": {
                "content": "TBL is commonly used to help individuals develop collaborative learning activities, but iterative TBL has been somewhat neglected in the literature. The authors introduce a framework for iterative TBL that sub-divides iterative TBL into 4 stages of group activity workflows and 3 data flows.",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
